# AI agents & LLM applications

- Tool schemas: validate inputs/outputs; timeouts; user-visible errors when tools fail.
- Treat untrusted documents and web fetches as injection sources; sandbox or strip when needed.
- Log trace/session IDs; keep eval golden sets under version control (no secrets in fixtures).
- Model/provider keys: env only; no logging of full prompts with PII in production without policy.
- Use `ai-agent-engineer` persona; infra with `devinfra-engineer`.
